# Job wizard forms

## Migration modes (4)

`HOT_ONLY`, `COLD_ONLY`, `HOT_THEN_COLD`, `COLD_THEN_HOT` — use `MIGRATION_MODE_OPTIONS`. Worker runs phases in order: `COLD_THEN_HOT` = cold then hot. Seed sessions map 1:1 via `LabSeedSessionService.mapScenario`.

## Reusable inputs

| Need | Component |
|------|-----------|
| Integer fields | `NumberInput` — never raw `type="number"` |
| Range datetimes | `DateTimeTzField` — UTC/IST, stores ISO UTC |
| Chunk durations | `DurationInput` — min/hr/day UI, API still `*ChunkDurationHours` |

## Hot/Cold step sections

`HotColdConfig` uses `FieldSet` + `FieldLegend`: Migration mode → Range → Timestamp → Chunk config.

## ON CONFLICT verify

- `POST /api/jobs/verify-conflict-index` — read-only `pg_index` check (PostgreSQL)
- Step 4 **Next** blocked until `conflictVerified`
- Logs via `LiveLogTerminal`; suggest `CREATE UNIQUE INDEX` on mismatch

## Wizard layout

- `WizardStepFooter` — sticky bottom nav on small screens
- Tab content: `flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col` + scrollable body

## Theming

Colors/layout via `apps/web/src/app/globals.css` semantic tokens — no raw color classes in new form code.
